text: Rhynchodes is a genus of beetles belonging to the family Curculionidae. They are restricted to New Zealand and New Caledonia. ==List of species== There are ten species: * Rhynchodes alboguttatus * Rhynchode ater * Rhynchodes eloini * Rhynchodes falleni * Rhynchodes jekeli * Rhynchodes rubipunctatus * Rhynchodes saundersii * Rhynchodes squameus * Rhynchodes ursus * Rhynchodes weberi ==Sources== Category:Cryptorhynchinae Category:Curculionidae genera Category:Beetles of New Zealand Category:Taxa named by Adam White (zoologist)
title: Rhynchodes
